701157f-a.title: Bronx: Grand Concourse - 165th Street (East)
701157f-a.text:
1040 to 1050 Grand Concourse (left), east side, north from East 165th, to but not including 166th Streets. Also shown (right) are Nos. 163 to 171 East 165th Street, adjoining and east of the N.E. corner of
Grand Concourse.
May 16. 1928.
P. L. Sperr.

701156f-a.title: Bronx: Grand Concourse - 165th Street
701156f-a.text:
1032 Grand Concourse, at the S.E. corner of East 165th Street, showing
the Ursuline Academy.
May 16, 1928.
P. L. Sperr.
